r blutwurst, bacon or chocolate… even president or ninja!<br></li><li>Run for your life and avoid getting sliced, chopped, burned, or smashed in this adventure run game!<br></li><li>Tons of juicy sausages to choose from and tons of hot dog skins to enjoy in this adventure run.<br></li><li>Compare the speed of your wursts in a classic Sausage Race or outrun a giant land mower in Panic Race!</li></ul>",
